description: America finally gets a taste of STI's special S-series WRXs. The last S-series WRX STI gets an HKS turbocharger, uprated fuel system, and a WRC-inspired intercooler water spray system to produce Subaru's most powerful boxer-4 ever: 341 horsepower and 450 newton-meters of torque. This is not only the first S-series STI to make it to the US, it is also the first not to be sold in Japan at all.
creator: Bnuuy
